【解】状态I（初态）参数计算：
$$
p_{\text{左}1} = \frac{M_{\text{左}}}{\mu} \frac{R T_{\text{左}1}}{V_{\text{左}1}} = 6\,\text{atm}
$$
由于$p_{\text{左}1}>p_{\text{右}1}=1\,\text{atm}$，隔板保持关闭。

状态II（隔板将开未开）：
\begin{align*}
p_{\text{右}I} V_{\text{右}1}^{5/3} &= p_{\text{右}II} V_{\text{右}II}^{5/3} \\
\Rightarrow V_{\text{右}II} &= 3.82\times10^3\,\text{cm}^3 \\
T_{\text{右}II} &= \frac{p_{\text{右}II} V_{\text{右}II} \mu}{M_{\text{右}} R} = 559\,\text{K}
\end{align*}
外界做功：
$$
A_{\text{I}\to\text{II}} = \Delta U = \frac{M_{\text{右}}}{\mu} c_V (T_{\text{右}II}-T_{\text{右}I}) = 1.80\times10^3\,\text{J}
$$

状态III（混合后）：
\begin{align*}
T_{\text{III}} &= \frac{M_{\text{左}}T_{\text{左}II} + M_{\text{右}}T_{\text{右}II}}{M_{\text{左}}+M_{\text{右}}} = 314\,\text{K} \\
V_{\text{III}} &= 1.50\times10^4\,\text{cm}^3 \\
p_{\text{III}} &= 6\,\text{atm}
\end{align*}

状态IV（终态）：
\begin{align*}
T_{\text{IV}} &= T_{\text{III}}\left(\frac{V_{\text{III}}}{V_{\text{IV}}}\right)^{2/3} = 381.7\,\text{K} \\
A_{\text{III}\to\text{IV}} &= (M_{\text{左}}+M_{\text{右}})c_V(T_{\text{IV}}-T_{\text{III}}) = 2.99\times10^3\,\text{J}
\end{align*}

总功计算：
\begin{align*}
A_{\text{总}} &= 1.80\times10^3\,\text{J} + 2.99\times10^3\,\text{J} = 4.79\times10^3\,\text{J} \\
A_{\text{大气}} &= 10\,\text{N/cm}^2 \times 100\,\text{cm}^2 \times 1.12\,\text{m} = 1.12\times10^3\,\text{J} \\
A_{\text{净}} &= 4.79\times10^3\,\text{J} - 1.12\times10^3\,\text{J} = 3.67\times10^3\,\text{J}
\end{align*}

